cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CL. 

The paper discusses the application of AI techniques, specifically deep learning, to a social problem, which suggests cs.AI as the most likely sub-category. The challenge involves reasoning and estimation, which are common topics in machine learning and natural language processing, indicating cs.LG and cs.CL as likely sub-categories. The use of a knowledge graph also suggests cs.SI and cs.IR as possible sub-categories.
